  <num>8-173.48</num>
  <heading>District tax exemptions.</heading>
  <para>
    <num>(a)</num>
    <text>The assets and income of the Authority shall be exempt from taxation by the District government.</text>
  </para>
  <para>
    <num>(b)</num>
    <text>Bonds issued by the Authority and the interest thereon are exempt from District taxation except estate, inheritance, and gift taxes.</text>
  </para>
